    .image
      %img{:src => image_url("infinity.svg")}
    .content
      %h2 Your product is everywhere
      %span Anyone can buy directly from your tweets or retweets!  It's also easy to share on Facebook and Pinterest.
  .point
    .image
      %img{:src => image_url("creditcard.svg")}
    .content
      %h2 One-click payments
      %span Your buyers don't have to re-enter payments on external sites.  Paying on Twitter is just one click!
  .point
    .image
      %img{:src => image_url("time.svg")}
    .content
      %h2 One minute setup
      %span Whether you're a hobbyist or professional, you can list anything in under a minute!
